author: Jeremy
title: Re: N ! Obamacare repeal would be ‘DEVASTATING’ for Disney princesses
text:
— T. Becket Adams (@BecketAdams) February 19, 2017 
The Left isn’t crazy or ridiculous or anything. No, sirree: This is what @Disney princesses could look like in 2017 without the #ACA : https://t.co/HVFLp7TlbB pic.twitter.com/aFauyRNwRi 
— MAKERS (@MAKERSwomen) February 22, 2017 
More from feminist outlet MAKERS : 
“The most important outcome for the images is that people don’t become desensitized by what’s happening in American politics at the moment,” [illustrator Maritza Lugo] told Forbes. “There is definitely a war being waged on women in this country, and these images shine a light on it.” 
With the Republican party working to dismantle the Affordable Care Act (ACA), Lugo seeks to shed light on the anxiety many women feel, hoping to use her illustrations to create a call to action for new audiences. These Disney Princess Drawings Show the DEVASTATING Effects Repealing Obamacare Will Have on Women https://t.co/QRDB8VG2Gp via @TeenVogue 
— Mitchell Sunderland (@mitchsunderland) February 10, 2017 Trending   
Just DEVASTATING, you guys. We are so devastated. Every woman needs to see these Disney princess illustrations that show what can happen if Obamacare is repealed: https://t.co/tRPha09eIG pic.twitter.com/KFMm6yX3Xx
